    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n6911" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὁρμαίνω</span></b>  (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὁρμάω</span>), ipf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὥρμαινε</span>,
          aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὥρμηνε</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">turn over</span>
          in the mind, <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">debate, ponder;</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κατὰ φρένα καὶ κατὰ θῡμόν, ἀνὰ θῡμόν</span>
            (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐνὶ</span>) <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">φρεσίν,
