          acc., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πόλεμον, πλόον, χαλεπὰ ἀλλήλοις</span>,
            <i><span class="en">Od. 3.151</span></i>; and by <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὅπως, ἢ.. ἦ</span>, etc., <i><span class="en">Il. 14.20</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Il.
          21.137</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
